PCOS affects up to 26% of Indian women of reproductive age, often linking obesity and infertility with symptoms like irregular periods and excess hair growth.

## Page 1: PCOS Kya Hai? Symptoms in Hindi-English
**PCOS/PCOD samajhiye—ek common hormonal problem jo Indian ladkiyon ko zyada affect karta hai.**

PCOS polycystic ovary syndrome hai, jisme ovaries mein chhote cysts bante hain, hormones imbalance hote hain.[3] India mein 6-26% young women ko hota hai, khas kar urban areas mein due to diet and stress.[2][1]

**Common symptoms (lakshanon ko pehchano):**
- Irregular ya missed periods (har mahine nahi aana).[4]
- Weight gain, khas kar pet par (obesity 37-62% cases mein).[5]
- Unwanted hair (hirsutism), acne, hair fall.[1]
- Thakaan, mood swings, infertility (bachche na hone ki pareshani).[6]

Early diagnosis se control ho sakta hai—doctor se ultrasound aur blood tests karwaiye.[5]

## Page 2: PCOS aur Obesity ka Connection
**Kyun badhta hai pet ka fat PCOS mein? Indian diet se kaise ladna hai.**

PCOS mein insulin resistance hota hai, jo sugar ko fat mein badalta hai—India mein 50% PCOS women obese hoti hain.[1][5] Yeh metabolic syndrome, diabetes risk badhata hai.

**Obesity badhane wale karan:**
- High-carb diet (roti, rice zyada).[5]
- Kam exercise, sedentary lifestyle.
- Family history aur stress.

**Simple tips:**
- 5% weight loss se periods regular ho jate hain (studies confirm).[5]
- Dal-chawal kam, veggies/protein zyada; 500 cal deficit daily.[7]

Humara protocol yahan strong hai—cinnamon/berberine se insulin control, 12 weeks mein blood sugar 20-30% girta hai.[8]

## Page 3: PCOS se Infertility—Bachche Kaise Paayein?
**PCOS mein pregnancy ruk kyun jati hai? Safe tarike bata rahe hain.**

PCOS top infertility cause hai India mein—irregular ovulation se egg nahi banta.[1] 70% cases mein obesity se link, lekin 70-80% conceive kar leti hain treatment se.[5]

**Karan aur asar:**
- High androgens egg quality kharab karte hain.
- Irregular cycles ovulation miss karwate hain.


